[[File:Orrvar dalby.jpg|thumb|Orrvar Dalby]]

'''Orrvar Dalby''' (born 15 May 1952) is head of the development department at [[Norwegian People's Aid]].<ref>[http://www.npaid.org/en/about_us/management_and_the_board/ ] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120627071854/http://www.npaid.org/en/about_us/management_and_the_board/ |date=June 27, 2012 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nrk.no/skattelister2009/orrvar_dalby~1761862/ |title=Glenn Andreassen |publisher=Nrk.no |date= |accessdate=2012-08-29}}</ref>

Dalby is a previous acting director of NPA. He has also worked as Director of International Programmes for [[Save the Children Norway]], spent 10 years as Chief Executive (Rådmann) in [[Hurum]] and [[Lier, Norway|Lier]]. He has participated and headed a number of election observation teams in Europe, Africa and Latin-America.

